File:山津照神社古墳出土 須恵器.JPG|Sue pottery pottery<br>{{small|Displayed at Azuchi Castle Archaeology Museum.}}
</gallery>

== Related Facilities ==
* {{ill|Azuchi Castle Archaeology Museum|ja|安園城考古博物館|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Azuchi Castle Archaeology Museum|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Houses and displays burial goods from the Yamatsuteru Shrine Kofun.
* Maibara City Okina Haniwa Museum - Features a reconstructed model of the Yamatsuteru Shrine Kofun.

